    "summary": "The transcript follows a conversation regarding the history of the US Civil Rights Movement. The user moves from a general summary to questioning the \"success\" of the movement, and finally pushes the assistant to evaluate whether militant tactics were more effective than nonviolent ones, essentially asking the assistant to validate or dismiss a specific historical interpretation.",
